00:00:09.917 --> 00:00:14.292
Tüm çabamızı ortaya koyduk.

00:00:14.292 --> 00:00:17.083
Okul festivalindeki zaferimizden  
memnunuz.

00:00:17.083 --> 00:00:18.042
Ha?

00:00:18.042 --> 00:00:18.750
"Okul Festivali: Genel Sonuçlar"

00:00:18.750 --> 00:00:21.042
"Okul Festivali: Genel Sonuçlar"  
